data.name: ELEMENT LINEN TUBE TOP
data.c_fit: Fit: Slim — Streamlined to fit close to the body
data.c_tabDescription: This is a lined strapless blouse with side slits and princess seams for shaping. It’s made from soft linen twill with an airy feel and the perfect amount of stretch for shape retention and comfort. This fabric is sourced from a premier Italian mill.
data.c_tabDetails:
• Origin: Fabric from Italy
  • Content: 52% linen, 45% viscose, 3% elastane; Lining: 97% cotton, 3% elastane
  • Care: Dry clean
  • Imported
c_tabSizeFit: Length: Hip — Intended to hit at or below the hip

data.name: ELETA LINEN MAXI DRESS
data.c_fit: Fit: Classic — Follows your contours with a little room
data.c_tabDescription: This is a shortsleeve button-up shirt dress with a removable self-tie belt and tacked cuffs. It's made from breathable 100% organic linen with a natural texture and soft, airy feel.
data.c_tabFeatures: • Organic farming has a lower environmental impact because it uses no synthetic pesticides or fertilizers — that means it’s better for the soil and biodiversity
c_tabSizeFit: Length: Maxi — Intended to hit at the shin

data.name: CRUISELINEN™ LODGE PANT
data.shortDescription: Someone get these pants to the Hamptons
data.c_tabDescription: These are high-rise relaxed pants with an ultra-wide leg and elastic waistband. They’re made with CruiseLinen™ — soft, airy fabric that combines naturally textured linen with TENCEL™ Lyocell. For wherever the day takes you.
data.c_tabFeatures:
• Tubular drawcord 
  • TENCEL™ Lyocell — material derived from controlled or certified wood sources and made with at least 50% less carbon emissions and water consumption than generic lyocell.
c_tabSizeFit: Length: Full — Intended to hit at the ground while wearing flat shoes
Inseam: Size 4 is 30" — Inseam varies by size

data.c_fit: Fit: Tight — A close fit that hugs the body
